Package: wayland-2-gnome
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Leriart <leriart@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Protocol-aware Wayland proxy translating wlr-layer-shell to GNOME Shell overlays
 Translates wlr-layer-shell protocol calls (used by Waybar, Rofi,
 nwg-dock) into standard XDG surfaces that GNOME Shell understands.
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.35)
